name: Empowered Waifu #3
description:
Description: "We Can Do It." There is nothing in this world that these waifus can't do for you.

Jean is a free spirit you can never tie down. But your bravery and creativity sow a golden seed of love in her heart. She silently admired your way of getting out of trouble, all your trick and scheme. And everytime you show your wit, her love grows.
